\c 18
\s Eria navaporofita vaBhaari
\s pagomo reKarimeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino mazuva mazhinji akati apfuura, shoko raJehovha rikasvika kuna Eria negore rechitatu, richiti, "Enda undozviratidza kuna Ahabhi; ndigotuma mvura panyika."
\v 2 Ipapo Eria akandozviratidza kuna Ahabhi. Zvino nzara yakanga yanyanya kwazvo paSamaria.
\v 3 Ahabhi akadana Obhadhiya, iye wakanga ari mutariri weimba yake. (Zvino Obhadhiya wakanga achitya Jehovha kwazvo;
\v 4 nokuti nenguva iyo Izebheri yaakaparadza nayo navaporofita vaJehovha, Obhadhia wakatora vaporofita vane zana, akavavanza makumi mashanu namakumi mashanuzve mubako, akavapa chingwa nemvura.)
\v 5 Zvino Ahabhi akati kuna Obhadhiya, "Famba nenyika, kumatsime emvura, nokuhova dzose; zvimwe tingawana bundo, tiraramise mabhiza namahesera,tirege kurashikirwa nezvipfuwo zvose."
\v 6 Naizvozvo vakagovana nyika, kuti va- fambe nayo; Ahabhi akaenda ari oga kuno rumwe rutivi, Obhadhiya akae- ndawo ari oga kuno rumwe rutivi.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Obhadhiya wakati ari pa- nzira, Eria akasangana naye; akamuziva, akawira pasi nechiso chake, akati, "Ndimi here, ishe wangu Eria?"
\p
\v 8 Iye akamupindura, akati, "Ndini; enda unoudza ishe wako, uti, Tarirai, Eria ari pano.'
\p
\v 9 Iye akati, "Ndatadzeiko, zvamoda kuisa muranda wenyu mumaoko aAhabhi, andiuraye?
\v 10 NaJehovha Mwari we- nyu mupenyu, hapano rudzi kana ushe kwaasina kutuma iye ishe wangu kukutsvakai; kana vakati, Haapo pano, wai- pikisa ushe uhwo kana rudzi urwo, kuti havana kukuwanai.'
\v 11 Zvino moti, Enda undoudza ishe wako, uti, Eria ari pano.'
\v 12 Zvimwe ndichangobva kwamuri, Mweya waJehovha ndokukuisai kwandi- singazivi; zvino kana ndikandoudza Aha- bhi, akakushayai, uchandiuraya, asi ini muranda wenyu ndinotya Jehovha kubva pauduku hwangu.
\v 13 Ishe wangu hamuna kuudzwa here zvandakaita panguva iya Izebheri yaakauraya nayo vaporofita va- Jehovha kuti ndakavanza vaporofita va- Jehovha, vane zana, makumi mashanu namakumi mashanu mubako, ndikavapa zvingwa nemvura?
\v 14 Zvino moti, Chi- ndoudza ishe wako,' uti, Eria ari pano.' " Iye uchandiuraya.
\p
\v 15 Eria akati, "NaJehovha wehondo mupenyu, iye wandimire pamberi pake, ndichazviratidza kwaari nhasi zvirokwa- zvo."
\v 16 Naizvozvo Obhadhiya akaenda kuna Ahabhi, akamuudza Ahabhi aka- ndosangana naEria.
\p
\v 17 Zvino Ahabhi wakati achiona Eria, Ahabhi akati kwaari, "Ndiwe here, iwe mutambudzi waIsiraeri?"
\v 18 Iye akati, "Ini handina kutambudza Isiraeri; asi ndiwe neimba yababa vako, nokuti makasiya mirairo yaJehovha, mukatevera vaBhaari.
\v 19 Naizvozvo zvino chituma vanhu uunganidze vaIsiraeri vose pagomo reKarimeri, navaporofita vaBhaari vana mazana mana vanodya patafura yaIzebheri,"
\p
\v 20 Naizvozvo Ahabhi akatuma vanhu kuvana vaIsiraeri vose, akaunganidza vaporofita pagomo reKarimeri.
\v 21 Zvino Eria akaswedera kuvanhu vose, akati, "Mucharamba muchifunga mifungo miviri kusvikira riniko? Kana Jehovha ari Mwari, mumutevere, kana ari Bhaari, mumutevere iye." Asi vanhu havana kupindura shoko rimwe.
\p
\v 22 Ipapo Eria akati kuvanhu, "Ini, iyeni ndoga, ndini ndasara kuvaporofita vaJehovha, asi vaporofita vaBhaari vanosvika varume vana mazana mana namakumi mashanu."
\v 23 Naizvozvo ngavatipe nzombe mbiri, ivo vazvitsaurire nzombe imwe, vaiguranye, vaiise pamusoro pehuni, asi varege kuisa moto pasi payo; neniwo ndichagadzira imwe nzombe, ndi- chiisa pamusoro pehuni, asi ndisingaisi moto pasi payo.
\v 24 Zvino imi mudane zita ramwari wenyu, ini ndidanewo zita raJehovha, Mwari unopindura nomoto, iye ngaave Mwari. Vanhu vose vakapindura, vakati, "Zvarehwa zvakanaka."
\p
\v 25 Ipapo Eria akati kuvaporofita va- Bhaari, -"Chizvitsaurirai nzombe imwe, mutange kuigadzira, nokuti muri vazhinji; mudane zita ramwari wenyu, asi murege kuisa moto pasi payo."
\p
\v 26 Ivo vakatora nzombe yavakanga vapiwa, vakaigadzira, vakadana zita raBhaari kubva mangwanani kusvikira masikati makuru, vachiti, "Bhaari, tinzwei!" Asi kwakanga kusine zwi kana unopindura. Vakapoteredza aritari yakanga yavakwa vachipembera.
\p
\v 27 Zvino panguva yamasikati makuru Eria akavaseka, akati, "Danidzirai kwazvo; nokuti mwari, zvimwe ari pakufunga, zvimwe waenda kumwe, zvimwe wafamba rwendo, kana zvimwe uvete hake, anofanira kumutswa."
\v 28 Ipapo vakadani- dzira kwazvo, vakazvicheka netsika dzavo neminondo namapfumo, kusvikira ropa richidzutuka kwavari.
\v 29 Masikati malwru akati apfuura, vakaporofita kusvikira panguva yokubayira chipo chamadekwana; asi kwakanga kusina zwi kana unopindura, kana wakanga achiteerera.
\p
\v 30 Ipapo Eria akati kuvanhu vose, "Swederai kwandiri," vanhu vose vaka- swedera kwaari. Zvino wakagadzira aritari yaJehovha yakanga yaputswa.
\p
\v 31 Eria akatora mabwe ane gumi namaviri akaenzana namarudzi avana vaJako- kko , , wakal athz a naehwilla, zvichinzi, "Zita rako richanzi Isiraeri."
\p
\v 32 Akavaka aritari namabwe iwayo nezita raJehovha, akachera goronga rakakomba aritari rakanga rakaenzana napangadzvarwa zviyero zviviri zvezviyo.
\p
\v 33 Akaronga huni, akaguranya nzombe, akaiisa pamusoro pehuni, akati, "Chizadzai zvirongo zvina nemvura, muidire pamusoro pechipiriso chinopiswa, napamusoro pehuni."
\v 34 Akati, "Itai izvozvo rwechipiri," vakazviita rwechipiri. Akati, "Itai izvozvo rwechitatu;" vakazviita rwechitatu.
\p
\v 35 Mvura ikayerera, ikapoteredza aritari; akazadza negorongawo nemvura.
\v 36 Nenguva yokubayira chipo chamadekwana, muporofita Eria akaswedera, akati, "Imi Jehovha, Mwari waAbhurahamu, nowaIsaka, nowaIsiraeri, uye kuti ini ndiri muranda wenyu, uye kuti ndakaita izvi zvose ndarairwa nemi.
\v 37 Ndinzwei Jehovha, ndinzwei, kuti vanhu ava vazive kuti imi Jehovha ndimi Mwari, uye kuti ndimi makadzosazve mwoyo yavo."
\v 38 Ipapo moto waJehovha wakaburuka, ukapedza chipiriso chinopiswa, nehuni, namabwe, neguruva, ukananzva mvura yakanga iri mugoronga.
\p
\v 39 Vanhu vose vakati vachizviona, vakawira pasi nezviso zvavo, vakati, "Jehovha ndiye Mwari, Jehovha ndiye Mwari!"
\p
\v 40 Eria akati kwavari, "Batai vaporofita vaBhaari, varege kupukunyuka kunyange nomumwe wavo." Vakavabata. Eria akaburuka navo kurukova Kishoni, akavaurayirapo.
\v 41 Eria akati kuna Ahabhi, "Chirongedzai, mudye, munwe, nokuti kuno kuunga kwemvura zhinji."
\p
\v 42 Naizvozvo Ahabhi akarongedza kundodya nokunwa. Eria akakwira pamusoro pegomo reKarimeri, akagwadamira pasi, akaisa chiso chake pakati pamabvi ake;
\v 43 akati kumuranda wake, "Chikwira zvino, utarire kurutivi rwegungwa." Akakwira akatarira, akati, "Hakuna chinhu." Akati, "Endazve, kanomwe."
\v 44 Zvino panguva yechinomwe akati, "Tarirai, kune gore duku, rinokwira richibva mugungwa, rakafanana nechanza chomunhu." Akati, "Enda, undoti kuna Ahabhi, `Sungai ngoro yenyu, muburuke, kuti murege kudzivirirwa nemvura.' "
\p
\v 45 Zvino nguva duku yakati yapfuura, denga rikasviba namakore nemhepo, mvura zhit* Ahabhi akaenda nengoro, akasvika Jezereeri.
\v 46 Ruoko rwaJehovha rukasimbisa Eria; akazvisunga chiwuno chake, akamhanya pamberi paAhabhi kusvikira pasuo reJezereeri.
